title: Intro Episode - Your Brokenness is Welcome Here
description:
Are you tired of comparison, competition, and exclusivity? Do you desire authentic community and intentional conversation? In her very first podcast, Jordan welcomes you as you are, not as you think you ought to be. 

In this first episode, learn what inspired Jordan’s international movement, Your Brokenness Is Welcome Here, and how she went from college girl with an Etsy shop to sought-after speaker, author, and now, podcaster. Be expectant to become equipped and empowered with practical tools to navigate relationships, business, and major life decisions. Join the community and tackle the journey of life with a few laughs, embarrassing moments, and vulnerability along the way. This is just the start of becoming the SHE you were always made to be.

 http://jordanleedooley.com/your-brokenness-is-welcome-here/

@Jordanleedooley

@Shepodcast
